subject: UEFA Champions League (Soccer)
Soccer
lead_paragraph: A.C. Milan failed to reach the Champions League quarterfinals for the fourth successive season, with Tottenham advancing with a 0-0 draw in London that protected a 1-0 first-leg advantage.
